_:N44917815c28c47378d8a9d82487756bb <http://schema.org/description> "The Office of Gas and Electricity Markets (Ofgem) regulates the monopoly companies which run the gas and electricity networks. It takes decisions on price controls and enforcement, acting in the interests of consumers and helping the industries to achieve environmental improvements. Ofgem is a non-ministerial department." .
